data.description: Great opportunity for investors or first-time home buyers looking to build sweat equity! Home has new furnace, water heater, fridge all replaced in 2023. Needs minor cosmetic updates, paint, carpet, and finishing touches to make it your personal home! Spacious three-bedroom, three-bath home on a corner lot in a lovely, established Victory neighborhood! The main level features a charming front porch, open floor plan, large living room, and spacious kitchen with center island. There are three bedrooms and two bathrooms on the upper level, including the owner's suite with private 3/4 bath and walk-in closet.
